skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: chicago hangs
des:
Chicago Hangs is a suggestion skill that recommends attractions and top places to visit while in town. The recommendations made also provide location and contact information.

You can ask "Alexa, ask Chicago hangs to tell me about Chicago" or "Alexa, ask Chicago Hangs to give me attractions."
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
